data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the picturesque South Venice area! This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. BRAND NEW ROOF IN SEPTEMBER 2023! Step inside and be greeted by the timeless allure of mostly tile floors, complemented by life-proof flooring in select spaces for easy maintenance. The spacious interior features a well-appointed kitchen, and a cozy living area that opens up to a tranquil backyard. What sets this property apart is the option for private boat ramp and ferry access through the South Venice Association, providing you with the unique opportunity to explore the waterways at your leisure. Whether you're a water sports enthusiast or simply seeking a peaceful retreat, this home offers a seamless blend of coastal living and modern comfort. Don't miss out on the chance to make this South Venice gem your own!
